law.history: Repealed 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 529, sec. 17, effective July 15, 1998; amended ch. 426, sec. 509, effective July 15, 1998. -- Created 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 368, sec. 9, effective January 16, 1991.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Agreement with Cabinet for Human Resources for enforcement purposes.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/98). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 529 prevails over its amendment in 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426.
